== 發現歷史 ==
副甲狀腺首次由[[理查·歐文|理查·歐文]]從[[印度犀牛|印度犀牛]]中發現<ref name="Cave1953">{{cite book |last=Cave |first=A.J.E. |editor=E. Ashworth Underwood |title=Science, Medicine and History. Essays on the Evolution of Scientific Thought and Medical Practice |accessdate=2009-07-20 |volume=2 |year=1953 |publisher=Oxford University Press |pages=217–222 |chapter=Richard Owen and the discovery of the parathyroid glands |chapterurl=http://www.rhinoresourcecenter.com/ref_files/1216989886.pdf |archive-date=2011-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715181948/http://www.rhinoresourcecenter.com/ref_files/1216989886.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，人體內的副甲狀腺最早由[[瑞典|瑞典]]醫學生Viktor Sandström (1852-1889)於1880年發現<ref name="pmid7485136">{{cite journal |author = Eknoyan G |title = A history of the parathyroid glands |journal = Am. J. Kidney Dis. |volume = 26 |issue = 5 |pages = 801–7 |pmid = 7485136 |doi = 10.1016/0272-6386(95)90447-6 |url = http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0272638695904476 |date = November 1995 |access-date = 2011-08-09 |archive-date = 2019-09-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190919043316/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0272638695904476 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 血液供應 ==
副甲狀腺的血液供應，一般來自[[甲狀腺下動脈|甲狀腺下動脈]]的主要分支、少數來自[[甲狀腺上動脈|甲狀腺上動脈]]。下副甲狀腺的血液供應則來自下副甲狀腺動脈，為甲狀腺下動脈的主要分支。異位於前縱膈的副甲狀腺，血供來自[[內乳動脈|內乳動脈]]。[[副甲狀腺靜脈|副甲狀腺靜脈]]一般匯入同側[[甲狀腺下靜脈|甲狀腺下靜脈]]。

